---
import BaseLayout from "@layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const pageTitle = "找不到頁面（404）｜香港共和國";
const pageDescription = "所請求的頁面不存在或已被移除。";
---

<BaseLayout title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription}>
  <section class="wrap">
    <div class="badge">系統提示</div>
    <h1>找不到頁面（404）</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      所請求的資源在此地址無法取得。請檢查網址是否正確，或使用下列官方入口返回。
    </p>

    <div class="panel">
      <div class="panel-head">
        <div class="panel-title">建議操作</div>
        <div class="panel-sub">官方導覽入口</div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid" aria-label="官方入口">
        <a class="tile" href="/HKR/">
          <div class="tile-title">首頁</div>
          <div class="tile-desc">返回官方門戶首頁</div>
        </a>

        <a class="tile" href="/HKR/press">
          <div class="tile-title">公告</div>
          <div class="tile-desc">政策發布、新聞稿與官方聲明</div>
        </a>

        <a class="tile" href="/HKR/government">
          <div class="tile-title">政府</div>
          <div class="tile-desc">憲制機關與公共機構概述</div>
        </a>

        <a class="tile" href="/HKR/laws">
          <div class="tile-title">法律</div>
          <div class="tile-desc">憲政框架與核心法規入口</div>
        </a>

        <a class="tile" href="/HKR/timeline">
          <div class="tile-title">年表</div>
          <div class="tile-desc">國史紀錄與重大事件</div>
        </a>

        <a class="tile" href="/HKR/symbols">
          <div class="tile-title">國家象徵</div>
          <div class="tile-desc">國旗、國徽與格言</div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="note">
      若您由外部連結進入此頁面，建議返回來源頁面並更新書籤或引用連結。
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    .wrap {
      max-width: 920px;
    }

    .badge {
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.8px;
      color: #fff;
      background: #111;
      padding: 0.25rem 0.55rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .lead {
      color: #444;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      max-width: 60rem;
    }

    .panel {
      margin-top: 1.3rem;
      border: 1px solid #e7e7e7;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: #fff;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .panel-head {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: baseline;
      gap: 1rem;
      padding: 1rem 1rem 0.85rem;
      background: #fafafa;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eeeeee;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .panel-title {
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: 0.2px;
    }

    .panel-sub {
      color: #666;
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .grid {
      padding: 1rem;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 0.8rem;
    }

    .tile {
      display: block;
      border: 1px solid #e7e7e7;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: #fafafa;
      padding: 0.95rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #111;
    }

    .tile:hover {
      border-color: #b80000;
      background: #fff;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 26px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
    }

    .tile-title {
      font-weight: 900;
      margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    }

    .tile-desc {
      color: #555;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .note {
      margin-top: 1.25rem;
      border: 1px solid #e7e7e7;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: #fafafa;
      padding: 0.95rem 1rem;
      color: #555;
      font-size: 0.98rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 980px) {
      .grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
